<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Account Suspended</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background: #f8f9fa;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      height: 100vh;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .suspended-container {
      background: #fff;
      padding: 40px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    h1 {
      color: #d9534f;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }
    .contact {
      margin-top: 30px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #777;
    }
    .contact a {
      color: #007bff;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .contact a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="suspended-container">
    <h1>Account Suspended</h1>
    <p>Your server account has been temporarily suspended due to outstanding payments.</p>
    <p>Please settle your balance to restore access to your services.</p>
    <div class="contact">
      For assistance, contact Vitarix Support at 
      <a href="mailto:support@vitarix.com">support@vitarix.com</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
